  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 2em;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><ms-cmark-node><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;font-weight: bold;font-style: italic;\">1.&nbsp;</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">进入 AgentDock 目录：</span></span></ms-cmark-node></p>\n    <p class=\"code-snippet__fix code-snippet__js\"></p>\n    <ul class=\"code-snippet__line-index code-snippet__js\"></ul>\n    <pre class=\"code-snippet__js\" data-lang=\"bash\"><code><span leaf=\"\"><span class=\"code-snippet__built_in\">cd</span>&nbsp;AgentDock</span></code></pre>\n    <p></p>\n    <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 2em;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><ms-cmark-node><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;font-weight: bold;font-style: italic;\">2.&nbsp;</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">一键启动所有服务：</span></span></ms-cmark-node></p>\n    <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 2em;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><ms-cmark-node><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">使用 docker-compose 命令启动管理面板、数据库和工具节点。</span></span></ms-cmark-node></p>\n    <p class=\"code-snippet__fix code-snippet__js\"></p>\n    <ul class=\"code-snippet__line-index code-snippet__js\"></ul>\n    <pre class=\"code-snippet__js\" data-lang=\"nginx\"><code><span leaf=\"\"><span class=\"code-snippet__attribute\">docker</span>&nbsp;compose up -d</span></code></pre>\n    <p></p>\n    <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 2em;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><ms-cmark-node><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">此命令会在后台启动所有必要的服务。您可以使用 docker ps 命令检查服务是否正常运行。</span></span></ms-cmark-node></p>\n    <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 2em;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><ms-cmark-node><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;font-weight: bold;font-style: italic;\">3.&nbsp;</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">验证部署：</span></span></ms-cmark-node></p>\n    <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 2em;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><ms-cmark-node><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">工具沙盒默认运行在 <a href=\"http://localhost:8000。\" target=\"_blank\">http://localhost:8000。</a></span></span></ms-cmark-node></p>\n    <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 2em;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><ms-cmark-node><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">您可以通过访问 <a href=\"http://localhost:8000/health\" target=\"_blank\">http://localhost:8000/health</a> 来检查服务是否健康。如果返回 JSON 格式的健康状态信息，则说明部署成功。</span></span></ms-cmark-node></p>\n    <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 2em;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><ms-cmark-node><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;font-weight: bold;\">③ 配置并运行智能体模型 AgentCPM-Explore</span></span></ms-cmark-node></p>\n    <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 2em;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><ms-cmark-node><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">文档推荐在预置的 Docker 评测环境中进行操作，以避免环境依赖问题。</span></span></ms-cmark-node></p>\n    <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 2em;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><ms-cmark-node><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;font-weight: bold;font-style: italic;\">1.&nbsp;</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">拉取并进入预置环境：</span></span></ms-cmark-node></p>\n    <p class=\"code-snippet__fix code-snippet__js\"></p>\n    <ul class=\"code-snippet__line-index code-snippet__js\"></ul>\n    <pre class=\"code-snippet__js\" data-lang=\"bash\"><code><span leaf=\"\"><span class=\"code-snippet__comment\"># 确保当前在 AgentCPM-Explore 项目根目录</span></span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\"><span class=\"code-snippet__comment\"># 拉取预置的 Docker 镜像</span></span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\">docker pull yuyangfu/agenttoleap-eval:v1.0</span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\"><span class=\"code-snippet__comment\"># 启动一个容器，并将当前目录映射到容器内</span></span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\">docker run -dit --name agenttoleap --gpus all --network host -v $(<span class=\"code-snippet__built_in\">pwd</span>):/workspace yuyangfu/agenttoleap-eval:v1.0</span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\"><span class=\"code-snippet__comment\"># 进入容器</span></span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\">docker&nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__built_in\">exec</span>&nbsp;-it agenttoleap /bin/bash</span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\"><span class=\"code-snippet__comment\"># 在容器内进入项目工作目录</span></span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\"><span class=\"code-snippet__built_in\">cd</span>&nbsp;/workspace</span></code><br></pre>\n    <p></p>\n    <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 2em;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><ms-cmark-node><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;font-weight: bold;font-style: italic;\">2.&nbsp;</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">配置运行参数：</span></span></ms-cmark-node></p>\n    <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 2em;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><ms-cmark-node><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">编辑项目根目录下的 quickstart.py 文件，找到 [USER CONFIGURATION] 部分，根据你的需求配置一下。</span></span></ms-cmark-node></p>\n    <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 2em;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><ms-cmark-node><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.11296296296296296\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100047041\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=1fc3daa6&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FePw3ZeGRruxnNFXx4BicdM4jHrVweHawKkTM70W4nJpw0qIu4Ebn7a17Ty9WU0p2tzfQ5HYk5kMx88RQVSsqkFw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></ms-cmark-node></p>\n    <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 2em;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><ms-cmark-node><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;font-weight: bold;font-style: italic;\">3.&nbsp;</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">运行智能体任务：</span></span></ms-cmark-node></p>\n    <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 2em;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><ms-cmark-node><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">完成配置后，运行 QuickStart 脚本。</span></span></ms-cmark-node></p>\n    <p class=\"code-snippet__fix code-snippet__js\"></p>\n    <ul class=\"code-snippet__line-index code-snippet__js\"></ul>\n    <pre class=\"code-snippet__js\" data-lang=\"nginx\"><code><span leaf=\"\"><span class=\"code-snippet__attribute\">python</span>&nbsp;quickstart.py</span></code></pre>\n    <p></p>\n    <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 2em;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><ms-cmark-node><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">脚本会自动执行您定义的任务，展示智能体的完整交互过程，比如思考、工具调用、结果生成。</span></span></ms-cmark-node></p>\n    <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 2em;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><ms-cmark-node><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;font-weight: bold;\">④ 查看运行结果</span></span></ms-cmark-node></p>\n    <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 2em;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><ms-cmark-node><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">任务执行完成后，结果会保存在 outputs/quickstart_results/ 目录下。</span></span></ms-cmark-node></p>\n    <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 2em;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><ms-cmark-node><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">您可以查看其中的 dialog.json 文件，它记录了完整的任务执行轨迹，包括智能体的思考链、每次工具调用的请求与响应以及最终答案。</span></span></ms-cmark-node></p>\n   </ms-cmark-node>\n  </ms-text-chunk>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "清华等机构联合开源 AgentCPM，这是一个仅 4B 参数却在长程深度探索任务上比肩 30B 级模型的端侧智能体，并提供了全套开发基础设施。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "清华等机构联合开源 AgentCPM，这是一个仅 4B 参数却在长程深度探索任务上比肩 30B 级模型的端侧智能体，并提供了全套开发基础设施。",
  "summary": "本文介绍了由清华大学、中国人民大学、面壁智能及 OpenBMB 联合推出的开源智能体项目 AgentCPM。该项目核心模型 AgentCPM-Explore 基于 Qwen3-4B 进行后训练，专注于解决长周期、多步交互的复杂任务。其显著特点是“以小博大”，在 4B 参数规模下，通过类人思考逻辑（如质疑工具、多源验证）实现了超越 8B 级 SOTA 甚至比肩部分闭源大模型的性能。此外，项目不仅开源了模型权重，还配套提供了 AgentDock（工具沙盒）、AgentRL（强化学习框架）和 AgentToLeaP（评测平台）等全套基础设施，极大降低了开发者复现和私有化部署端侧智能体的门槛。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "AgentCPM 以 4B 参数规模实现了极高的长程任务处理能力。",
      "explanation": "模型支持超过 100 轮的稳定环境交互，在 Xbench-DeepResearch 等高难度智能体任务榜单上表现优于部分闭源大模型。"
    },
    {
      "point": "该模型具备类人思考逻辑，而非简单的模式记忆。",
      "explanation": "AgentCPM 能够主动核查信息、质疑工具输出并灵活调整策略，展现出类似经验丰富研究员的深度探索特质。"
    },
    {
      "point": "项目提供了从模型到工具链的全栈开源基础设施。",
      "explanation": "包含 AgentDock 沙盒管理、AgentRL 强化学习框架及评测平台，支持开发者进行完整的二开和私有化部署。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "仅 4B 参数的模型，在复杂的长程深度探索任务上，实现了超越同尺寸 SOTA、甚至比肩 30B 级和部分闭源大模型的性能。",
    "它是首个具备 GAIA、Xbench、Browsercomp 等 8 个高难度智能体任务处理能力的 4B 端侧模型。",
    "它支持最高超过 100 轮的不重复且稳定的环境交互，能够持续深度探索直至任务完成。",
    "具备质疑工具、追求原始数据、灵活调整策略及执着寻找信源等特征的类人思考逻辑。",
    "AgentCPM 不仅开源了模型权重，还开源了从 Base 模型进化到 SOTA 模型的全套基础设施。"
  ],
